{"variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"occ"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnannotationview\/rotatestomatchcamera"]}],"primaryContentSections":[{"declarations":[{"tokens":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"@property"},{"kind":"text","text":" ("},{"kind":"keyword","text":"nonatomic"},{"kind":"text","text":", "},{"kind":"keyword","text":"assign"},{"kind":"text","text":") "},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"BOOL","preciseIdentifier":"c:@T@BOOL"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"rotatesToMatchCamera"},{"kind":"text","text":";"}],"platforms":["iOS"],"languages":["occ"]}],"kind":"declarations"},{"content":[{"type":"heading","anchor":"discussion","text":"Discussion","level":2},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"When the value of this property is "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"YES"},{"type":"text","text":" and the map is rotated, the annotation"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"view rotates. This is also the behavior of "},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotationImage"},{"type":"text","text":" objects. When the"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"value of this property is "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"NO"},{"type":"text","text":" the annotation has its rotation angle fixed."}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"The default value of this property is ","type":"text"},{"code":"NO","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":". Set this property to ","type":"text"},{"code":"YES","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" if the","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"view’s rotation is important.","type":"text"}]}],"kind":"content"}],"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre","doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotationView"]]},"metadata":{"remoteSource":{"url":"https:\/\/github.com\/maplibre\/maplibre-native\/blob\/main\/platform\/ios\/src\/MLNAnnotationView.h#L193","fileName":"MLNAnnotationView.h"},"modules":[{"name":"MapLibre"}],"role":"symbol","symbolKind":"property","externalID":"c:objc(cs)MLNAnnotationView(py)rotatesToMatchCamera","title":"rotatesToMatchCamera","fragments":[{"text":"rotatesToMatchCamera","kind":"identifier"}],"navigatorTitle":[{"text":"rotatesToMatchCamera","kind":"identifier"}],"roleHeading":"Instance Property"},"identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"occ","url":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotationView\/rotatesToMatchCamera"},"schemaVersion":{"major":0,"minor":3,"patch":0},"kind":"symbol","abstract":[{"text":"A Boolean value that determines whether the annotation view rotates together","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"with the map.","type":"text"}],"sections":[],"references":{"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNAnnotation":{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotation","type":"topic","kind":"symbol","title":"MLNAnnotation","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnannotation","abstract":[{"text":"The ","type":"text"},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotation","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"text":" protocol is used to provide annotation-related information","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"to a map view. To use this protocol, you adopt it in any custom objects that","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"store or represent annotation data. Each object then serves as the source of","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"information about a single map annotation and provides critical information,"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"such as the annotation’s location on the map. Annotation objects do not provide"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"the visual representation of the annotation but typically coordinate (in"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"conjunction with the map view’s delegate) the creation of an appropriate"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"objects to handle the display."}],"fragments":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"MLNAnnotation"}],"role":"symbol"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNAnnotationImage":{"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"The "},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotationImage"},{"type":"text","text":" class is responsible for presenting point-based"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"annotations visually on a map view. Annotation image objects wrap "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"UIImage"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"objects and may be recycled later and put into a reuse queue that is maintained"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"by the map view."}],"role":"symbol","type":"topic","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnannotationimage","kind":"symbol","title":"MLNAnnotationImage","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotationImage","fragments":[{"text":"MLNAnnotationImage","kind":"identifier"}]},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNAnnotationView":{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotationView","title":"MLNAnnotationView","role":"symbol","kind":"symbol","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnannotationview","fragments":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"MLNAnnotationView"}],"type":"topic","abstract":[{"text":"The ","type":"text"},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotationView","isActive":true,"type":"reference"},{"text":" class is responsible for marking a point annotation","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"with a view. Annotation views represent an annotation object, which is an","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"object that corresponds to the ","type":"text"},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotation","isActive":true,"type":"reference"},{"text":" protocol. When an annotation’s","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"geographic coordinate is visible in the map view, the map view asks its","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"delegate to a corresponding annotation view. If an annotation view is created","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"with a reuse identifier, the map view may recycle the view when it goes","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"offscreen.","type":"text"}]},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNAnnotationView/rotatesToMatchCamera":{"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"A Boolean value that determines whether the annotation view rotates together"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"with the map."}],"fragments":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"rotatesToMatchCamera"}],"role":"symbol","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotationView\/rotatesToMatchCamera","type":"topic","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnannotationview\/rotatestomatchcamera","title":"rotatesToMatchCamera","kind":"symbol"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre":{"url":"\/documentation\/maplibre","abstract":[{"text":"Powerful, free and open-source mapping toolkit with full control over data sources and styling.","type":"text"}],"kind":"symbol","title":"MapLibre","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre","type":"topic","role":"collection"}}}